result.name: Mellow Brown Coffee, Sogo, Causeway Bay

reviews.text: Excellent service smile 😊 friendly staffs.  Good service
Nice coffee shop. Tasty food
Tried the seafood rice dish (forgot what it was called). Felt like there were more ingredients than rice, which was good. Served piping hot. I love it.
Tried the breakfast, not bad! Good coffee!

Goog to have tea time here, but not so good for anything else. The glass is so dirty, even request for having another glass of water, it remained the same. The previous cafe called Sogo Cafe offered so much better overall dining experience, from food quality,  taste, and service hospitality perspective. They should really not neglect one simple thing - the water. I dont expect they serve coffee with mineral water, but it must be clean enough not to spoil the coffee original taste. They have changed new glasses, but water quality remained to be disappointing

result.name: SOGO Causeway Bay

reviews.text: This is a big department store. Beautiful, fashionable, practical  things can be found there. There is also a big supermarket in the basement where people can get delicious  food and drinks. It is sure a good place to visit.👍👍👍👍

Their supermarket has quality items and their food court has lots to offer with quality food too. The shopping mall has good brands to offer but I am used to the Philippines' mall, where it is spacious that I can choose different brands in one floor because here you have to go to several floors to go to different brands.
U can buy everything u want there! May and Nov got thankful week, the week that has crazy discount! Which also means super crowded period during thankful week.

Seriously people come here to buy things. Not for shopping experience. More than 10 floors are packed with merchandise and buyers that you could not move easily. But they sell everything you would need and conveniently located above mtr stations, with a bunch of bus routes stop in front of the shop and located in the center of causeway bay area. One of the busiest area in Hong Kong island
It’s a good shopping center. It has most brands you want. The basement has a decent supermarket with many snack stands. If you have time you should go.

reviews.text: Excellent service smile 😊 friendly staffs.  Good service
座位比較少，所以等位時間比較長。味道好，但價錢中上。
星期日下午2:30-6:00也有下午茶包一杯咖啡。意粉水準不俗。加十元由蒸餾咖啡變Cappuccino。
Le seul intérêt de ce lieu est de permettre une pause au cœur du gigantesque magasin Sogo. Service un peu mou.
我老公鐘意埃塞俄比亞咖啡多過blue mountain no.1
